{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"criteria":[{"citation":{"description":"_criterion_id now contains the project- -> project. mapping (lines 84-87); run_case at line 246 calls this and dispatches to _run_criterion_case instead of raising 'no eval solver'.","kind":"file","line_end":88,"line_start":66,"path":"src/rebar/llm/evals/eval_solver.py"},"criterion":"`rebar criteria eval <project.criterion>` resolves and runs the project criterion's Pass-1 finder over its dataset (no `no eval solver` error), for a criterion whose logical id contains the `project.` namespace dot.","kind":"codebase-verifiable","met":true},{"citation":{"description":"Sibling file test_eval_solver_project_criterion.py contains test_criterion_id_resolves_namespaced_project, test_run_case_resolves_namespaced_project, and test_calibrate_resolves_namespaced_project — all using FakeRunner with an injected tmp project.testcrit overlay.","kind":"file","line_end":118,"line_start":1,"path":"tests/unit/test_eval_solver_project_criterion.py"},"criterion":"A regression test drives `calibrate_criterion` (or `eval_solver.run_case`) for an activated `project.<name>` criterion with an injected/fake runner and asserts the criterion resolves (fires/does-not-fire per the fake), proving the physical→logical round-trip. File: `tests/unit/test_criteria_eval.py` (or a sibling).","kind":"codebase-verifiable","met":true},{"citation":{"description":"test_calibrate_perfect_criterion_kappa_one and test_calibrate_n_run_stability both call calibrate_criterion('F1', ...) with injected solve, asserting correct recall/kappa/stability for the built-in F1 criterion.","kind":"file","line_end":115,"line_start":75,"path":"tests/unit/test_criteria_eval.py"},"criterion":"Built-in criterion calibration (e.g. `F1`) is unchanged (no regression).","kind":"codebase-verifiable","met":true}],"findings":[],"material_fingerprint":null,"model":"anthropic:claude-sonnet-4-6","runner":"pydantic_ai","schema":"completion_verifier_pass_v1","ticket_id":"2340-1b72-109a-43d7","verdict":"PASS"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMPLETION_VERDICT","timestamp":1784269445695562001,"uuid":"1698384f-7161-4d9c-8371-07c13f462af2"}